snippet: The Knicks got another strong game from guard Jeremy Lin, who scored 23 points and had 10 assists as they beat Washington.
abstract: New York Knicks defeat Washington Wizards, 107-93; Knicks have won three straight games since Jeremy Lin joined the rotation as point guard.
lead_paragraph: The Knicks got another strong game from guard Jeremy Lin, who scored 23 points and had 10 assists as they beat Washington.

headline.seo: Jeremy Lin Leads Knicks Again, 107-93, Over Wizards
headline.main: Lin Leads Again as Knicks Win 3rd in Row
headline.print_headline: Lin Leads Again as Knicks Win 3rd in Row
